.TH wsp-registry 1  "registry " 
.SH NAME
registry \- Manage the global repo registry
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBregistry\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Manage the global repo registry
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
registry\-add(1)
Register and bare\-clone a repository
.TP
registry\-ls(1)
List registered repositories [read\-only]
.TP
registry\-rm(1)
Remove a repository and its mirror
.TP
registry\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
